sequenceDiagram
    participant UI as Angular UI
    participant ALB as ALB (path routing)
    participant VS as dpay-validation-service
    participant CS as wdpr-config-services
    participant SNS as SNS: validation-events

    UI->>ALB: POST /api/v1/validations/evaluate
    ALB->>VS: Route to validation service

    VS->>VS: Parse and validate request schema
    VS->>CS: GET /configs/{clientId}/rules
    CS-->>VS: Configuration rules + thresholds

    VS->>CS: GET /configs/{clientId}/state (target env)
    CS-->>VS: Current config state

    VS->>VS: Evaluate rules against config state
    VS->>VS: Generate validation report

    alt All rules pass
        VS->>SNS: Publish validation.completed
        VS-->>ALB: 200 {valid: true, report}
        ALB-->>UI: 200 OK
    else Rules violated
        VS->>SNS: Publish validation.failed
        VS-->>ALB: 200 {valid: false, violations[]}
        ALB-->>UI: 200 OK (with violations)
    end
